c: 30
v: 23
t: "wmn dalayil hadhih alqudrat 'ana jaeal allah alnwm raht lakum fi allayl 'aw alnhar; 'iidh fi alnwm husul alrrahat wdhhab alteb, wajaeal lakum alnahar tantashirun fih litalab alrzq, 'iina fi dhalik ldlayl ealaa kamal qudrat allah wnfwdh mshyyth liqawm yasmaeun almwaez smae tamal wtfkr waetbar"